nodes.text: A unidentified warehouse on Level 1315 in the underworld of the planet Coruscant housed boxes of Nano-droids.

Around 20 BBY, Jedi Padawan Ahsoka Tano was framed for the murder of Letta Turmond—the female that orchestrated an attack on the Jedi Temple by feeding Nano-droids to her Abyssin husband, Jackar Bowmani.

The fugitive Tano—aided by the bounty hunter Asajj Ventress—journeyed to this warehouse to inspect the place for the droids that Turmond had used. But Ventress was attacked by Barriss Offee who stole her twin lightsabers and then attacked Tano in the warehouse. Barriss Offee then vanished, and Tano was stunned into submission by clone Commander Wolffe, who was on the hunt for her along with Jedi Master Plo Koon, Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker and Captain Rex.
